OL,6,FBodycam footage released by
OL,7,FNorthumbria Police captures the moment
OL,8,Fan officer had hot oil thrown towards
OL,9,Fthem
OL,11,FPolice have released body camera
OL,12,Ffootage of the aftermath of an officer
OL,13,Fbeing doused in hot oil while trying
OL,14,Fto make an arrest.
OL,16,FMohammed Sarfaraz, 45, of Kingston
OL,17,FPark Road, Gosforth, Newcastle, was
OL,18,Fjailed at Newcastle Crown Court for
OL,19,Fnine years, Northumbria Police said.
