OL,6,FThe incident happened in January when
OL,7,Ffive officers went to speak to him
OL,8,Fabout a criminal allegation and they
OL,9,Flocated him inside a property where he
OL,10,Fbegan to make verbal threats.
OL,12,FDespite officers' attempts to de-
OL,13,Fescalate the situation, he threw a pan
OL,14,Fof hot cooking oil towards their
OL,15,Ffaces, hitting two of them and causing
OL,16,Fscars to one.
OL,18,FSarfaraz then barricaded himself in
OL,19,Fthe garage where he was tasered and
OL,20,Farrested.
