OL,6,FHe was charged the next day with
OL,7,Faffray, attempting to cause grievous
OL,8,Fbodily harm with intent and causing
OL,9,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent, and
OL,10,Fwas convicted following a trial.
OL,12,FNorthumbria Police said one of the
OL,13,Fvictims sustained second and third
OL,14,Fdegree burns on his skin, leaving him
OL,15,Fwith scarring on his face and chest.
OL,17,FAfter sentencing, Detective Inspector
OL,18,FMarc Lennox said: "This was a shocking
OL,19,Fincident, which saw Mohammed Sarfaraz
OL,20,Fattack officers who were attempting to
OL,21,Fspeak with him.
