OL,6,FDet Insp Lennox added: "I would like
OL,7,Fto commend those officers involved for
OL,8,Ftheir bravery and professionalism in
OL,9,Fwhat must have been a fast-moving and
OL,10,Fterrifying incident.
OL,12,F"I'm pleased to see that Sarfaraz will
OL,13,Fnow spend a lengthy spell behind bars
OL,14,F` while the victims continue to move
OL,15,Fforward with their duties."
